s: I bought this aqua lounge for my husband as a gift after the ones that we had before finally had to be thrown out. The material is great, BUT the foot and base where you blow up the tubes to insert are garbage. They need to be blown up every time we use them becuuse the tubes just pop open at the valves and let the air out with any pressure from laying on them. The quality just isn't as good. Go with a different brand...
